00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Welcome to our panel on the foundation model economy.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,500
It's not a feature you bolt on at the end, it's the architecture you start from.

3
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:13,000
If you're building here, you need to focus on unit economics.

4
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:17,000
The risk is that inference cost eats your margin.

5
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,500
But who actually owns the model weights?

6
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:25,000
For example, look at what the open source labs are doing.
